{"tid":1142703,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【誰是兇手】爆拍劇遭老前輩「鹹豬手」 姚樂怡反擊：Body Check呀？","createTime":"2019-05-07T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T10:16:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd215fa3f6c2dc2c46a22096d372d11c8217938","tid":1142703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"現年45歲的姚樂怡出道時憑34C豐滿上圍而受注目，15年她為老公生下囡囡Gaibe，身材依然沒有走樣。<br />\n近日樂怡聯同「七魔女」成員文頌嫻、梁靖琪及鍾麗淇，為另一魔女成員周家蔚與劉永健主持的ViuTV節目《友枱VIP》擔任嘉賓，眾人傾偈時，話題扯到曾否被男藝人「抽水」，眾魔女都表示有類似經歷，其中樂怡更分享她擊退「鹹豬手」的招數：「舊時拍劇有個老前輩傾偈嗰時會有意無意咁摸身摸勢，我咪笑住同佢講：『唔好Body Check我啦老爺！』之後有場戲見到佢，佢又想摸我，我就再講：『你又Body Check呀？』佢呢次就知我話緊佢，以後唔敢亂嚟。」<br />\n樂怡與「七魔女」經常聚會見面，樂怡於節目中大爆家蔚喝酒後會含情脈脈地望住她，尤如把她當成愛人，但其他姊妹就反擊指樂怡每次都以駕車為由不飲酒，又齊齊投訴樂怡專拍下她們酒後失儀行為。不過，樂怡解釋她只是一番好意，希望一班姊妹知道自己酒後模樣作警惕之用。<br />\n另外，文頌嫻曾先後在無綫和亞視拍劇，節目中她被問到兩台文化有何不同時，文頌嫻指亞視許多監製和導演也是電影界紅人，所以演員拍劇都要遷就幕後製作人員檔期，相反無綫聘用較多新人，所以演員自主權相對較大。<br />\n《蘋果》記者曾致電樂怡，欲了解那位前輩「鹹豬手」，她笑說：「唔記得喇。都唔會講喇。」記者再致電周家蔚問「鹹豬手」是誰，但她表示不清楚：「唔知喎，佢冇講到邊個喎，真係冇講喎。我哋都想知邊個，但事後完全唔記得咗問返佢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557212728_02fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557212728_02fa.jpg&h=adf9ff9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557211577_c482.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557211577_c482.jpg&h=021fe407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190507/59573263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59573263&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=0ba81c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59573263&h=830bf945\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190507/59573263</a>"},{"pid":"0bbe9c197f3a667f5a5415e079070d6715aa009c","tid":1142703,"uid":214036,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85e64062d13740dfe658ed62aeb6c0f59b2a2d0e","tid":1142703,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"691bc51c5fb7b122dd3f99942169d961ceb2729a","tid":1142703,"uid":120955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔係龍就係鼠㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254918503f5a6d25f0ee8ec6172f35a568425eaa","tid":1142703,"uid":13914,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"想同佢+文頌嫻3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf72915ad5261c4d8717659bc075dd738ad55941","tid":1142703,"uid":151926,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"x子x"},{"pid":"749572e27c123edb2485d5f508868d156bbce4a3","tid":1142703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f65d9970c5a8c7822f4b5d52c3f34daaab2739a3","tid":1142703,"uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0bbe9c197f3a667f5a5415e079070d6715aa009c","tid":1142703,"uid":214036,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"直接爆埋角色<br />\n搵下邊個演過佢老爺就知"},{"pid":"2e610e7c912abf7a4874a87477aa2fdbbe05b0da","tid":1142703,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"冇曾生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7566301e4257623cfd49cdf299da4253a48d7eac","tid":1142703,"uid":124655,"like":1,"d